Package hc.server.ui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CtrlResponse
    CtrlResponse is used for designing a remote controller.
    HTMLMlet
    HTMLMlet displays JComponents as HTML on mobile (not snapshot), you can set CSS for these JComponents.

    Not all HTML tag are supported in mobile runtime environment.
    Mlet
    Mlet is an instance running in HomeCenter server, and the snapshot of Mlet is presented on mobile.
    ProjectContext
    There is only a ProjectContext instance for each HAR Project at runtime.
